    <p class="section-number">05, Where we go</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">ILVE service across Greater Los Angeles.</h2>

    <p>ILVE installations cluster in specific demographics across our 5-county service area. Bel Air, Beverly Hills, Holmby Hills, and Hancock Park anchor the highest-volume Majestic II 90cm and 120cm professional range installations — kitchens designed around the Italian aesthetic where ILVE won the spec over Wolf or Thermador on design grounds. The Nostalgie collection specifically shows up in Hancock Park, Larchmont, and Pasadena historic-home renovations where vintage-style design was the deciding factor. Bel Air and Brentwood pick up custom-color Majestic installations matched to specific kitchen palettes. Pacific Palisades and Malibu coastal-property installations occasionally use ILVE outdoor-adjacent or summer-kitchen applications. Encino and Sherman Oaks see the Professional Plus configuration in larger Spanish Revival kitchens. The 8-branch dispatch grid in the hero CTA shows the closest dispatch territory; our technician arrives at diagnostic with common ILVE gaskets and igniters on the truck — major components ship from Italy via ILVE USA distribution and we set the timeline expectation at diagnostic.</p>
